data.description: Discover this 3-bedroom, 2 bathrooms, poured concrete and block construction home, with a 2-car garage.  Featuring a metal roof from 2020, waterfall quartz countertops in the kitchen, an open floor plan, new light fixtures, and a bonus Florida room with beautiful a decorative ceiling. Bring your boat, toys, and chickens; this home has room for them all. The location is hard to beat, an A rated school system, only miles from the beach, walking distance to restaurants, shops, and all the fun that downtown Jensen Beach has to offer, this home proves to be a real gem!
